members.name: enabled
members.doc: Whether the item is set to allow preordering.

members.name: message
members.doc: A message that buyer will see when the item is out of stock and PreOrder enabled

members.name: limit
members.doc: Number of products that can be preordered after stock reaches zero.

members.name: variants
members.doc: Variants associated with this inventory item.

members.name: numericId
members.doc:
Inventory’s unique numeric ID (assigned in ascending order).
 Primarily for sorting and filtering when crawling all inventories.

members.name: inStock
members.doc: Whether the product is listed as in stock.

members.name: quantity
members.doc: Quantity currently left in inventory (only returned when inventory is being tracked).

members.name: inStock
members.doc: Whether the product variant is in stock.

members.name: limit
members.doc: Amount of items to load per page

members.name: offset
